Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • InteractionDesign.Group3.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Record>

    public class Record
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Record>
    Represents the weather forecast at a particular time. Stores the temperature, weather icon, and a time stamp. I think this will need expanding so we have enough data to recommend items.
